     F** AGDR02 ************************************************
     F* IAF PRODUCTION PLACE OPERATION CALENDAR  - CREATE-     *
     F* S.YAMAGAMI   90.12.25                                  *
     F* -----------------------------------                    *
     F* TCHK1 10/13/11 CHG F8YOBI=6,7 '*'-->F8HIRU,F8YORU      *
JW1  F* JW    10/17/17 SET DEFAULT VALUE TO @KAISI/@OWARI      *
JW2  F* JW    06/19/18 ADD OVERWRITTEN FILE                    *
JW3  F* JW    09/06/18 CHG/ADD MESSAGE                         *
JW4  F* JW    12/06/22 ADD LOG FILE (AGDPP15)                  *
     A**********************************************************
     FAGDPW02 CF  E                    WORKSTN
JW2  FAGDPL12 UF  E           K        DISK         KINFDS INF1  A
     FAGDPL22 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
JW4  FAGDPP15 O   E                    DISK
JW3  E                    ER      1  10 60
      ******
      * DS *
      ******
      *
JW2  IINF1        DS
 |   I                                        1  10 PF
 |   I                                       83  84 OV2
 |   I                                       83  92 OVPF
JW2  I                                       93 102 OBLIB
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60@NENG
     I                                        1   40NEN
     I                                        5   60TSUKI
     I              '(ASJ CALENDAR)     ' C         TITL#
     I              '(FORECAST CALENDAR)' C         TITL@
     I              '(REGULAR CALENDAR) ' C         TITL$
     I              '(IAF PRODUCTION )  ' C         TITL
      *
JW4  I            DS
 .   I                                        1  140SDATE
 .   I                                        1   60NOW
 .   I                                        7  140TODAY
 .   I                                        7  120YYMM
 .   I           SDS
 .   I                                        1   8 #PGM
 .   I                                      244 253 #WSID
JW4  I                                      254 263 #USER
      ********
